167319.「我が名は アサヒ……\n あまつちに 雷鳴轟かせる者たちの末裔。:
My name is Asahi...descendant of those who
roared thunder in the land of the living.

167321.「クスクス……さかしいな。\n それでこそ 八卦で 見定めたかいがある。:
That's funny. That's why it's worth using the
bagua to find out.

167322.「クスクス……それでよい。\n そなたに 知らしめるために 呼んだのだから。:
Kusum Kusum...that's good. I called you here
to let you know.

167323.「……とくと 見届けよ。\n 我ら 天地雷鳴士の みわざを！: Behold! The deeds of our druid!

167329.「ねえっ ケガしてない！？ 風邪ひいてない！？\n 魂 とびだしてない！？:
Hey, you're not hurt! You haven't caught a
cold! You didn't start your soul!

167330.「ほ ほんとに ごめんね……。\n キミを襲うつもりは なかったの！: I'm so, so sorry... I didn't mean to hurt you!

167331.「あっ！ あらためて 自己紹介させて！\n あたしは アサヒ！: Ah! Let me introduce myself again! I'm Asahi!

167332.「おちゃめなエルフっ子は 世を忍ぶ仮の姿……:
The mischievous Elf girl is a mask for the
world...

167333.「その正体は天地雷鳴士 陽衆の頭領だよ！\n まいったか！！:
His true identity is Druid, the chieftain of
the Yang Clan! Oh, no!

167334.「そして ここは 陽衆の隠れ家なの！\n じゃじゃーーーん！！: And this is the Yang Clan Hideout! Ta-da!

167335.「あはは！ すこーし さびれてるでしょ！\n 今じゃ 一族は 数人しかいなくて！:
Ha-ha-ha! You must be a little rusty! There's
only a few of us left!

167337.「あたしの家 陽衆は…… \n エルトナの歴史の陰で 都を守り続けてきた\n 天:
My family, the Yang Clan, is the family of the
druids who have been protecting the city in
the shadows of Eltona's history!

167338.「天地雷鳴士とは 光と陰のはざまに生ける職業。 \n あまつちにまつわる術を あ:
Druid is a profession that lives between light and shadow. They can control the arts related to the earth and call Famililar called Phantom
Demons!

167339.「はるか昔 カミハルムイの都は\n 千夜嵐という みぞうの天変地異に襲われてね。:
A long time ago, the city of Kamiharmui was
struck by a storm of a thousand nights, a
natural calamity.

167340.「その時 千夜嵐を退けたのが ご先祖さま！:
Then, the ancestors repelled the storm of a
thousand nights!

167341.「だけど……時代とともに 忘れ去られて \n 数を減らしていって……\n 今では:
But... over time, they have been forgotten and
their numbers have dwindled... and nowadays
few persons even know their names!

167342.「ゆーえーにー！ あたし 決めちゃった！！: Yeeeeeeeeeeee! I've made up my mind!

167343.「あたしの代で 天地雷鳴士を\n バイーンと 盛りあげようって！！:
I'm going to make Druid a big success in my
generation!

167344.「古い慣習なんて 脱ぎすてちゃって\n なうで やんぐな イケてる人を\n 天地:
Let's get rid of the old conventions and
recruit some yang, yang, yang hot persons to
join Druid!

167345.「そんでね！ 八卦っていう占いをしたら \n <pc>という名前の 奇異な星のも:
And then! I did a divination called Bagua and it showed that a person born under a strange star named will visit Royal
City!

167346.「もー この人しかいない！ って \n ビビっと来ちゃったの 霊感的なアレが！:
Mmm, he's the only one! That's when I got a
jolt of inspiration!

167347.「それで……あの……\n キミを呼びだして 天地雷鳴士の\n すごいところを 見:
So...um...I was going to call you over and
show you what a druid you are, but...

167348.「その……まだまだ 未熟で…… \n 幻魔が言うこと聞かなくて あんな事故に……:
I'm still a little inexperienced... and the
phantom didn't listen to me... and that's why
we had that accident.

167350.「あっ あたしってば……\n 期待の新人さんを 落水させて……:
Oh, I'm sorry... but I let a promising
newcomer fall in the water...

167351.「おまけに 幻魔のシュジャクちゃんも\n 逃げちゃって……:
In addition, Peashock, the phantom demon, ran
away...

167352.「これって お家断絶かもーーーーー！？: This could be the end of the family!
